Book 3 Started &amp; Finished June 3rd 2020
Review 4/5
Thoughts Similar to Recursion, Dark Matter is yet another sci-fi thriller. Although the plot was slightly less convoluting, I felt a stronger connection to each of the characters. This book is a fun read and I recommend it for anyone interested in science fiction and mystery. Revolving on the idea of regret, the book provides a unique take on those moments when we wonder what if&hellip;
